273
00:26:15,770 --> 00:26:18,609
Aku tidak tahu dan khawatir sekali.

274
00:26:20,050 --> 00:26:21,709
Kenapa kamu khawatir?

275
00:26:23,179 --> 00:26:24,850
Coba pikirkan.

276
00:26:25,219 --> 00:26:27,449
