279
00:26:35,629 --> 00:26:36,629
Baiklah.

280
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:39,600
Pulanglah lebih dahulu.

281
00:26:43,869 --> 00:26:45,340
Kamu mau ke mana?

282
00:26:45,340 --> 00:26:47,639
Aku mau menjenguk Sang Goo dan mendoakannya cepat sembuh.

283
00:28:06,949 --> 00:28:09,689
"Hold Me Tight"

